verses.text:
For he built again the high places which Hezekiah his father had destroyed;
and he raised up altars for Baal, and made an Asherah, as Ahab king of Israel did, and worshipped all
the army of the sky, and served them.

He set the engraved image of Asherah that he had made in the house of
which the LORD said to David and to Solomon his son, “In this house, and in Jerusalem, which I have chosen
out of all the tribes of Israel, I will put my name forever;

“Because Manasseh king of Judah has done these abominations, and has
done wickedly above all that the Amorites did, who were before him, and has also made Judah to sin with
his idols;
